Package: portableIRTEngine
Title: Portable SSQ-10 IRT Harmonization Engine
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "CO-LUMINATE",
      family = "DSU Team",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "dsu@ahri.org"
    )
  )
Description: Packages the selected Objective 3 SSQ-10 harmonization engine
    into a reusable R scoring core with a Shiny front end scaffold. The tool
    applies a fixed-parameter IRT scoring engine to new SSQ-10 data, returns
    harmonized theta scores, maps those scores back to PHQ-oriented outputs,
    and applies stored binary depression cutoffs.
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: false
Depends:
    R (>= 4.2.0)
Imports:
    shiny,
    mirt,
    stats,
    utils
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
